errors.why-is-this-secret-unavailable: He aha tēnei karere huna kāore e wātea?
errors.secrets-are-designed-to-be-viewed-only-o: Kua hoahoatia ngā karere huna kia kitea kotahi noa te wā. Kua urunga pea tēnei hononga, kua pau, kua mukua ā-ringa rānei e te kaituku.
errors.contact-the-person-who-sent-you-this-lin: Whakapā atu ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga, ā, tonoa ki te waihanga i tētahi karere huna hou. Kia mōhio rātou kāore koe i taea te uru ki ngā mōhiohio taketake.
errors.oops-the-page-you-are-looking-for-doesnt: Auē! Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei.
errors.if-youre-unsure-what-to-do-next-please-f: Mēnā kāore koe e tino mōhio me aha koe ā muri ake nei, tēnā whai ake ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga mō ētahi atu mōhiohio.
errors.information-shared-through-our-service-c: Ko ngā mōhiohio i tuari mā tā mātou ratonga ka taea te uru kotahi anake. Ka tirohia ana, ka mukua pūmautia te ihirangi mai i ā mātou tūmau hei whakaū i te noho muna. Ka āwhina tēnei huarahi ki te tiaki i ō raraunga tairongo mā te whakawhāiti i tōna whakaaturanga me te ārai i te urunga whakaaetia-kore.
errors.were-sorry-but-an-unexpected-error-occur: E whakapāha ana mātou, engari i puta he hapa ohorere i te wā o te tukatuka i tō tono. Kua whakamōhiotia tō mātou rōpū, ā, kei te mahi mātou ki te whakatika.
errors.go-share-a-secret: Haere tuari i tētahi karere huna!
errors.the-page-youre-looking-for-doesnt-exist-: Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei. Kaua e māharahara, ka pā tēnei ki te pai rawa o tātou!
errors.unable-to-load-data-due-to-data-format-i: Kāore e taea te uta raraunga nā ngā take whakatakotoranga raraunga. Tēnā ngana anō ā muri ake.
